content.text: Reminder - I have a vet appointment for Max next Tuesday at 3pm. He needs his annual shots. Also I need to set up my new work laptop this weekend - DataFlow uses MacBook Pro M4 Max.

Got it! Two things on the radar:

2. Set up DataFlow MacBook Pro M4 Max this weekend

Want me to help with the laptop setup when you're ready?
